inv_downtime=spark.sql("select * from reassets.invperformance order by date desc")
#display(inv_downtime)
inv_downtime=inv_downtime.toPandas()
inv_downtime["Date"]=inv_downtime["Date"].astype("datetime64[ns]")
inv_downtime=inv_downtime.head(80).copy()
Blocklist=[]
for i in range(len(inv_downtime)):
    if inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0] in ["I08","I10","I12","I13"]:
        #print(inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0])
        Blocklist.append("Antpr1")
    elif inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0] in ["I16","I17","I18","I19"]:
        #print(inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0])
        Blocklist.append("Antpr2")
    elif inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0] in ["I01","I02","I03","I04"]:
        #print(inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0])
        Blocklist.append("Antpr3")
    elif inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0] in ["I11","I14","I15","I20"]:
        #print(inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0])
        Blocklist.append("Antpr4")
    elif inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0] in ["I05","I06","I07","I09"]:
        #print(inv_downtime.iloc[i,2].split("_")[0])
        Blocklist.append("Antpr5")
Blocklist
